Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.00,0:00:07.50,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Can't you see that you are sweet？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.50,0:00:16.20,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Oh Let me love you so
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.50,0:00:30.50,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}見上げる空は遠いけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.50,0:00:37.50,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}抱えきれない夢がある
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.50,0:00:38.50,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そうよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.10,0:00:44.50,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}創られた世界の中を
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.50,0:00:52.50,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}抜け出して　自由になりたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.50,0:00:59.50,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}走り続けて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.50,0:01:05.50,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}空に屆けば
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.50,0:01:11.00,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}風になれると
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.50,0:01:17.00,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そう信じてるから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.50,0:01:23.50,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I never give up forever
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.69,0:02:06.38,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說謊 巴尼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.49,0:02:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,報告 "路比根"作戰失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.49,0:02:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高達依然在Side6
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.69,0:02:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"塞庫羅普斯"小隊生死不明,完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.51,0:02:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 馬上停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.91,0:02:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.31,0:02:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是中校的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.51,0:02:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,齊！這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.91,0:02:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.02,0:02:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得沒有允許使用核子彈頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.22,0:02:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也記得 沒得到允許啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.82,0:02:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢夥 要無視條約嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.62,0:02:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Side6並未參與南極條約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.33,0:02:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那個問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.03,0:02:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我的行動是將軍管轄之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.63,0:02:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的指揮權在我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.44,0:02:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將軍！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.58,0:03:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作業繼續開始進行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.48,0:03:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從此刻格瑞那達由我指揮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.89,0:03:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.19,0:03:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想和你直接談談的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.69,0:03:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪兒呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.09,0:03:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在吉翁的機動戰士旁邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.29,0:03:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何說要在哪裡和你會面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.32,0:03:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼可愛的小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.22,0:03:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然是那個機動戰士的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.22,0:03:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.93,0:03:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打倒這機動戰士的也是你吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.03,0:03:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.63,0:03:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有殘存的兩名吉翁士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.43,0:04:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,往市外逃了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.17,0:04:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼還記得的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.67,0:04:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒有什麼特別的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.37,0:04:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼樣的事都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.77,0:04:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在抱歉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.58,0:04:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次的襲擊據說有內部人的接應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.78,0:04:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於此事有什麼想法嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.59,0:04:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有想到是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.29,0:04:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白跑了一趟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.59,0:04:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.99,0:04:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.29,0:04:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些人再行動的話又會有人死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.10,0:04:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是還真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.90,0:04:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明是中立衛星殖民地的此處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.40,0:04:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然會被吉翁的機動戰士如此大膽的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.10,0:04:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是為什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.51,0:04:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.71,0:04:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.81,0:04:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道而不能回答 是吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.51,0:04:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以聯邦軍駐留在此為名目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.92,0:04:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秘密在此開發機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.92,0:04:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以吉翁才來的 不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.32,0:04:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.13,0:04:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死亡人數246名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.03,0:05:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重輕傷者572名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.16,0:05:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是昨天的受害者的數目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.67,0:05:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望不要再發生這種大慘事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.37,0:05:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如不迎戰 會死更多人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.67,0:05:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是沒辦法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.68,0:05:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想說的我很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.08,0:05:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒辦法而不得不犧牲的人 應該一個也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.48,0:05:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是數目的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.70,0:05:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這真是慘 怎麼會這樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.00,0:05:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殘存的吉翁士兵逃到市內了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.81,0:05:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不好 被我看到一定打死他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.51,0:05:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在沒必要在衛星殖民地內打嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.51,0:05:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦到底在幹些什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.31,0:05:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.51,0:05:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.88,0:06:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼 那傢夥 高達如何了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.19,0:06:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它 已被米舍破壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.20,0:06:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也儘快逃脫吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.70,0:06:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼 慌話說得真差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.71,0:06:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隊長！隊長！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.21,0:06:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隊長！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.15,0:07:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡提 西太卡死了阿！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.26,0:07:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米舍呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.56,0:07:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那黑頭發的年輕人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.73,0:07:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也戰死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.96,0:07:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.06,0:07:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後你就用那護照逃脫吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.57,0:07:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盡可能快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.47,0:07:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是想等警戒鬆了之後才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.87,0:07:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 要馬上逃脫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.37,0:07:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想等一陣子比較安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.48,0:07:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.58,0:07:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.08,0:07:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好聽著！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.19,0:07:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在聖誕夜之前不能消滅高達的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.69,0:07:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格瑞那達的艦隊會來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.99,0:07:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使用核子武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.69,0:07:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連同衛星殖民地一起轟掉的作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.49,0:07:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會那樣，不可能的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.90,0:07:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.70,0:07:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之 快逃 逃走活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.40,0:07:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不逃嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.74,0:08:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經很老了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.65,0:08:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我很喜歡這個衛星殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.96,0:08:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼 是我啦 巴尼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.67,0:08:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有注意你身後 走過來的時候沒人跟蹤？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.11,0:08:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.57,0:08:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察有在找我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.78,0:08:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.78,0:08:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐嘛 吃吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.08,0:08:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.09,0:08:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人很容易就會死的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.80,0:08:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是那些話 不要再去想了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.30,0:08:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.50,0:09:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死去的人就怪他們運氣差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.94,0:09:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管什麼是隊長或什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.74,0:09:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有運氣就會死！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.24,0:09:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.94,0:09:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.50,0:09:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.45,0:09:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來！吃吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.85,0:09:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.76,0:09:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在今天之內會逃離這個衛星殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.36,0:09:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要逃嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.46,0:09:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.16,0:09:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 那傢夥 聯邦的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.57,0:09:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.47,0:09:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要放棄嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.17,0:09:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是瞭解你的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.67,0:09:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時逃也是男人作為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.47,0:09:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.17,0:09:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且這樣下去 死去的人又算什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.48,0:09:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你聽聽我的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.78,0:09:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再過三天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.28,0:09:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如不在聖誕夜前解決高達的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.98,0:09:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格瑞那達的艦隊會來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.89,0:09:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使用核子武器連同這個衛星殖民地一起轟掉的作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.09,0:09:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.09,0:09:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個衛星殖民地一定會被破壞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.09,0:10:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.20,0:10:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也快離開這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.00,0:10:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和你母親去旅遊吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.60,0:10:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是在聖誕夜前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.30,0:10:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把那傢夥打倒不就好了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.40,0:10:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能辦的到嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.00,0:10:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的 巴尼一定可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.31,0:10:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.31,0:10:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個怪物要如何才能打敗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.71,0:10:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖是新型也不過只是快一點而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.31,0:10:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個渣古只要修理一下也能...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.11,0:10:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修理之後又如何？你去操縱嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.32,0:10:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我連一架機動戰士也沒打下過啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.12,0:10:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說再打下一架就能成為王牌的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.93,0:10:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.13,0:10:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.03,0:10:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是一支菜鳥是大家的負擔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.83,0:10:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是被帶來的而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.13,0:10:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.64,0:10:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼一定是怕那傢夥才說謊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.74,0:10:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊！我很怕 不怕的話又怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.34,0:10:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任你說我膽小 什麼都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.34,0:10:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.65,0:10:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要煩 適可而止吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.45,0:10:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼 事實上是很強的吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.75,0:10:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能打倒它的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.99,0:11:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看 這是竊聽用的麥克風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.30,0:11:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為防止你會把我們的事傳出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.80,0:11:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用這個在竊聽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.70,0:11:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼夥伴的標誌 那是騙人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.61,0:11:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想活下去就要逃阿 亞爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.71,0:11:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從這個衛星殖民地逃走吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.31,0:11:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他人會怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.42,0:11:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高達 由我們來打倒它吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.32,0:11:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.02,0:11:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我決定要逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.13,0:11:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼是混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.14,0:11:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去警察局全抖出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.55,0:11:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做會被判死刑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.28,0:12:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是同罪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.21,0:12:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真爽！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.33,0:12:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子 怎麼不去學校？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.73,0:12:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是同罪！死刑啊！死刑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.04,0:12:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.04,0:13:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.02,0:13:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.52,0:13:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？有什麼擔心的事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.22,0:13:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.62,0:13:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都好 可以談談嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.83,0:13:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 巴尼怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.53,0:13:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近都看不到他啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.33,0:14:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道 那傢夥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.77,0:14:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.87,0:14:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 如果 只是如果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.88,0:14:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙艦隊攻過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.58,0:14:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個衛星殖民地要被毀滅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.18,0:14:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克莉斯會怎麼做？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.88,0:14:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我會戰鬥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.49,0:14:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不逃嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.69,0:14:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊！我想我是不會逃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.39,0:14:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不怕嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.89,0:14:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想是會怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.76,0:14:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但怕能夠忍受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.60,0:14:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孤獨就無法忍受了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.00,0:14:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孤獨？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.00,0:14:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,母親 父親 還有亞爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.20,0:14:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.91,0:14:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我重要的朋友都死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.41,0:14:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我一個人活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.91,0:14:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己一個人逃了 我自己是無法一個人活著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.31,0:14:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然逃跑是卑鄙的行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.92,0:14:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.52,0:14:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要戰鬥終究還是為自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.22,0:14:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為怕自己成為孤獨的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.03,0:14:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才會去戰鬥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.23,0:15:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那是我的生存方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.06,0:15:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃也屬於那個人的生存方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.87,0:15:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰都無法決定誰對 誰錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.07,0:15:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為戰爭就會有人死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.67,0:15:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不戰爭也是一樣會死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.58,0:15:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正確的事在哪兒都是不存在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.18,0:15:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能做自己能做的事而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.98,0:15:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說了些無關的事了 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.39,0:15:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.39,0:15:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碰到巴尼向他問好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.11,0:15:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佈雷 亞爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.52,0:15:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要到哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.82,0:15:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡都好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.82,0:15:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你啊！在這戰時怎麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.27,0:16:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,往法蘭茄斯卡 一張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.17,0:16:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,費用52O亥特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.49,0:16:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！不可以進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.19,0:16:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放手！健呢？德爾可呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.19,0:16:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.19,0:16:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道！不知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.59,0:16:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 回去！回去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.40,0:16:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！傻瓜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.20,0:16:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！喂！你們也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.70,0:16:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,適可而止些！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.81,0:16:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,健 德爾可 喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.51,0:16:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是亞爾嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.81,0:16:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.95,0:17:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天沒來學校吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.15,0:17:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很厲害啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.55,0:17:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉翁的機動戰士跑來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.45,0:17:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把學校破壞了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.56,0:17:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.76,0:17:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家？大家是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.06,0:17:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在學校的大家都沒事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.46,0:17:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是傻子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.86,0:17:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士來得時候是晚上啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.17,0:17:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.97,0:17:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你說我昨天沒去學校 我才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.47,0:17:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是來了呦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.38,0:17:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在攻擊完了之後馬上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.38,0:17:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.78,0:17:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你看看好玩的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.19,0:17:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是今天的收穫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.59,0:17:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,味道還留在上面阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.69,0:17:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要聞聞看嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.19,0:17:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要那種臉嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.70,0:17:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也會給你一點嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.60,0:17:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾 怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.60,0:17:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭嘛，振作點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.51,0:18:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西要多少有多少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.75,0:18:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對嘛 要笑嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.86,0:18:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長 有齊穆中校通信進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.07,0:18:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.27,0:18:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出擊時刻決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.37,0:18:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12月25日0時00分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.98,0:18:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛彈現在在裝配中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.28,0:18:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,齊穆 真的要用那個嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.38,0:18:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你反對司令部的決定嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.99,0:18:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.49,0:18:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你很能幹才派下的任務啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.89,0:18:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.80,0:18:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你成功！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.64,0:19:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？這樣裝如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.14,0:19:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要把過去到現在的事全說出來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.44,0:19:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話會瞭解我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.84,0:19:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼死刑嘛 為不讓自己孤獨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.75,0:19:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下不得了 馬上逃跑才行啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.65,0:19:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.85,0:19:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.15,0:19:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才叫你快跑呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.26,0:19:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的在聖誕夜吉翁的艦隊會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.76,0:19:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊~！知道了 知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.56,0:19:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不得了，不得了哦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.46,0:19:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信我嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.86,0:19:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你上次不是說什麼肇事逃跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.97,0:19:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,製造麻煩的小孩吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.67,0:19:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.97,0:19:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次是真的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.87,0:19:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了吧！可以回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.67,0:19:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫你父母來噢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.57,0:19:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都會死啊 笨蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.88,0:19:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會死的 我不管了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.88,0:19:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法蘭茄斯卡機MDW2O5班次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.59,0:19:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請指引乘客登機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.49,0:20:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,登機手續於3O分鐘後開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.21,0:20:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克莉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.12,0:20:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.32,0:20:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要點什麼飲料？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.73,0:20:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個……給我威士卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.83,0:20:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請稍候！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.23,0:20:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也再來威士卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.73,0:20:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,客人 不要再喝了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.84,0:20:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.84,0:20:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的人可以 我不能喝嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.74,0:20:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,威士卡是吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.54,0:20:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雙份！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.85,0:20:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3亥特5克魯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.69,0:21:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.80,0:21:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,費用我放在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.91,0:21:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊！是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.81,0:21:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照你所說，我正要出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.51,0:21:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到烏魯亞西的法蘭茄斯卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.12,0:21:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想我這麻煩要走 放心了吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.42,0:21:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和那女孩幸福的生活吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.52,0:21:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒病 只是稍微喝了點酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.63,0:21:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就沒醉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.13,0:21:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能醉得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.33,0:21:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說要結婚的不是你嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.54,0:21:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 說了一堆謊話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.05,0:22:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一點也不想去那種地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.98,0:22:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法蘭茄斯卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.98,0:22:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法蘭茄斯卡不是最差勁的衛星殖民地嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.89,0:22:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MDW2O5班機登機手續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.49,0:22:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.29,0:22:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次也是用馬上會被揭穿的謊言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.49,0:22:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像那女的說了吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.50,0:22:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我那時一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.40,0:22:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有把謊說下去的勇氣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.90,0:22:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙人 事實是很強的吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.70,0:22:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼 你贏得了那傢夥嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.31,0:22:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我喜歡這個衛星殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.11,0:22:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,容易？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.93,0:22:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在吃之前告訴你有關爸爸的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.84,0:22:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要離婚嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.64,0:23:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣 爸爸要回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.78,0:23:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.98,0:23:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶誕節的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.48,0:23:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要待到什麼時候？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.88,0:23:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直待下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.88,0:23:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽跟爸爸和好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.59,0:23:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 不高興嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.89,0:23:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從此以後一家三口一起生活哦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.40,0:23:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸要回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.61,0:23:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連爸爸都會死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.61,0:23:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都會死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.81,0:23:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.52,0:23:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有電話 叫巴尼的打來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.13,0:24:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.77,0:24:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼！是巴尼嗎？巴尼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.77,0:24:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，是我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.77,0:24:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼 那個…剛才對不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.28,0:24:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 救救我們好嗎？巴尼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.88,0:24:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩！我正打算這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.59,0:24:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.69,0:24:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊！為打倒它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.99,0:24:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我準備再做一次攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.19,0:24:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能幫我忙嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.99,0:24:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩！那當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.70,0:24:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真謝謝 巴尼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.50,0:24:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人一起做一定會很順利的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:34.90,0:24:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩！會很順利的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:38.10,0:24:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡你 巴尼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.71,0:24:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:20.80,0:25:27.31,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}噓をついた夜には
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:27.51,0:25:33.31,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}眠れずに　怖かった
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:34.00,0:25:39.00,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どんな喧嘩をしても
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:40.30,0:25:47.00,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}次の日は　忘れていた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:48.30,0:25:53.80,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}空が　青いこと
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:55.00,0:26:00.31,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}それが　嬉しくて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:01.70,0:26:08.00,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつか人を疑い
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:08.70,0:26:14.31,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生きる寂しさ知る事も
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:14.90,0:26:20.31,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}気がつかずに全てを
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:21.60,0:26:26.31,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}信じてた頃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:52.91,0:26:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬克其中尉 出擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:56.01,0:26:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:57.21,0:26:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,武器不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:59.41,0:27:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像在尋寶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:02.05,0:27:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在森林和它作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:14.56,0:27:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:18.26,0:27:21.00,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,口袋裏的戰爭